WEBVTT

00:00:00.997 --> 00:00:04.000
Outside of Philadelphia,

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:09.130
there is an old nursing home
that peaks out from behind lush trees.

00:00:10.173 --> 00:00:16.220
Instead of caring for the old,
these days, it detains the young.

00:00:17.096 --> 00:00:21.100
Kids who came to the United States
with their parents.

00:00:22.477 --> 00:00:23.895
Inside its hallways,

00:00:23.936 --> 00:00:27.607
a little boy named Diego
went from diapers to detention.

00:00:28.524 --> 00:00:30.401
When he was just one year old,